<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yuǎn zài tā xiāng wǒ sī niàn gù xiāng yuè, yuǎn zài tā xiāng wǒ sī niàn gù xiāng qíng
 dàn wǒ bù huì wàng jì nǐ men de zhǔ tuō dàn wǒ bù huì wàng jì nǐ men de dīng níng,
 xiào fǎ yé sū wàng wǒ de shě jǐ, xiào fǎ yé sū ài rén de shēng mìng
 rú ruò qīn rén lái xiāng wèn, yī piàn zhōng chéng yī piàn zhōng chéng.</lyrics>
